{"word":"H7763 - שֹׁומֵר - Shôwmêr - sho-mare' - Shomer","slug":"H7763","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שֹׁומֵר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shôwmêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sho-mare'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shomer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁמר שׁומר</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>shômêr shômêr</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>sho-mare'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Shomer = \"keeper\" <ol><li>son of Jehozabad or Shimrith the Moabitess and one of the conspirators who slew king Joash of Judah</li><li>an Asherite, son of Heber<ol type='a'><li>also 'Shemer'</li></ol></li></ol> <p />Origin: act part of <a href=\"#/H8104\">H8104</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3461\">H3461</a>, <a href=\"#/H4929\">H4929</a>, <a href=\"#/H4931\">H4931</a>, <a href=\"#/H8104\">H8104</a>, <a href=\"#/H8106\">H8106</a>, <a href=\"#/H8107\">H8107</a>, <a href=\"#/H8108\">H8108</a>, <a href=\"#/H8109\">H8109</a>, <a href=\"#/H8110\">H8110</a>, <a href=\"#/H8111\">H8111</a>, <a href=\"#/H8112\">H8112</a>, <a href=\"#/H8113\">H8113</a>, <a href=\"#/H8114\">H8114</a>, <a href=\"#/H8116\">H8116</a>, <a href=\"#/H8117\">H8117</a>, <a href=\"#/H8118\">H8118</a>, <a href=\"#/H8119\">H8119</a>, <a href=\"#/H821\">H821</a>"}]}